        "publishedAt": null,
        "description": "I wrote my senior thesis on the presence of misreporting and its effects and causes in private label MBS under the direction of Professors Richard Stanton and Nancy Wallace at the Walter A. Haas School of Business. It is still work in progress. At the core of the project is the analysis of massive databases of information regarding mortgage loans (Lewtan's ABSNet and Dataquick) and cross referencing to detect any differences in capital structure, occupancy and appraisal overstatement."
